{"tid":2173853,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"柏林影展宣布明年起不再區分男女演員獎","createTime":"2020-08-25T13:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T00:40:49.000Z","uid":352783,"like":9,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ef07f948fb56304ca128912ccaa12eb6155025bd","tid":2173853,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEnh66A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDEnh66A.jpg&h=5b8cafb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國柏林影展主辦單位宣布，最佳演員的「銀熊獎」，明年起將不再分男演員和女演員，只會頒發最佳主角和最佳配角獎，以減低性別色彩。<br />\n<br />\n荷里活早前爆出多宗嚴重性侵及性騷擾醜聞，震撼電影界外，隨之掀起的「#MeToo」性別平權運動也席捲全球。<br />\n<br />\n柏林影展的聲明表示，停止頒發區分性別的獎項，代表「電影產業釋出更具性別敏感意識的訊號」。<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位又說，明年影展將由2月11日至21日以「實體」方式舉行，並將採取措施，確保所有嘉賓可以盡最大可能出席。至於影展詳情未來幾星期公布。<br />\n<br />\n柏林影展、康城影展和及威尼斯影展並列歐洲3大影展，目前其他兩個影展仍然頒發男女最佳演員獎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545832-20200825.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545832-20200825.htm&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=643e77b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545832-20200825.htm&h=67644423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545832-20200825.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ec520b2b829b4f1d7216653182026f2cf618b602","tid":2173853,"uid":34869,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"頒少一半獎<br />\n然後頒比男又嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04af823461cd9bebfb67ad4a642595ab270bf52d","tid":2173853,"uid":68598,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"ec520b2b829b4f1d7216653182026f2cf618b602","tid":2173853,"uid":34869,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"頒少一半獎<br />\n然後頒比男又嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\